ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v231.message

Class ORR_O02

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractMessage
          • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v231.message.ORR_O02
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Message, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class ORR_O02
extends AbstractMessage

    Represents a ORR_O02 message structure (see chapter 4.2.2). This structure contains the following elements:

    • 1: MSH (MSH - message header segment)
    • 2: MSA (MSA - message acknowledgment segment)
    • 3: ERR (ERR - error segment) optional
    • 4: NTE (NTE - notes and comments segment) optional repeating
    • 5: ORR_O02_PIDNTEORCOBRRQDRQ1RXOODSODTNTECTI (a Group object) optional
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
